<plot>Ex-government spy Jefferson Keyes is an always-in-demand private investigator who will travel anywhere in the world to take a case. His fee is a cool one million dollars, which includes a guarantee of success, or else the fee is refunded. He operates out of Lincoln, Nebraska with Elena, the telephone operator who knows how to contact Keyes, and Tony, the pilot of his private jet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?115151</url></doc>
